uk.co.strangeskies.collection

Interface Reiterator<T,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of event message to consume
    R - the type of event message to produce
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.function.Consumer<T>, java.lang.Iterable<R>, java.util.function.Supplier<R>

    public interface Reiterator<T,R>
extends java.util.function.Consumer<T>, java.util.function.Supplier<R>, java.lang.Iterable<R>
    A buffer to decouple the delivery of events with their sequential consumption, such that events consumed will be queued for later supply.
